{"tid":566053,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］電視機雪花問題","createTime":"2018-02-19T14:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T08:46:42.000Z","uid":92397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d01d58f3090612fee4600caadc1c156ea3a105a","tid":566053,"uid":92397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"朋友剛入搬唐樓（太子）<br />\n<br />\n電視收得好差<br />\n<br />\n第一次自動搜台 一個台都冇<br />\n<br />\n第二次就只係搵到一個模擬台cctvb 起曬雪花<br />\n<br />\n第三次有三個模擬台 但除左cctvb 其他蒙到唔知咩台黎 <br />\n<br />\n總結都係一高清台都冇 <br />\n<br />\n已經教左搜索模擬&amp;數位<br />\n<br />\n電視已經插入 air 個個位<br />\n<br />\n究竟重有冇得救？<br />\n<br />\n買個放大器有冇幫忙？"},{"pid":"99fe6da482d740b841f6001420514c925f7a324a","tid":566053,"uid":92397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T08:32:21.000Z","msg":"求全能既連登仔解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcde80c25f6c46b6b1d99287161aec5e577a7130","tid":566053,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T08:38:57.000Z","msg":"你有冇插天線架 ?"},{"pid":"9f2d0b79ad5c00887ad022c4410b595545ba170d","tid":566053,"uid":163078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"第一，你要搞清楚你牆身天線位（拆面板睇）有冇接駁好／鬆咗。<br />\n第二，你要檢查單位接駁大廈天線個位有冇接駁得唔好。<br />\n第三，換另一條線試下。"}]}